{"tid":1254113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[贏]  家樂福中國8成股權 48億人民幣賣給蘇寧易購","createTime":"2019-06-24T02:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T00:58:54.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe8954b00adbfdcb534b7e4eb3b42fa4e6fa30e","tid":1254113,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:57:40.000Z","msg":"家樂福中國8成股權 48億人民幣賣給蘇寧易購<br />\n<br />\n（法新社巴黎23日電） 法國超市巨擘家樂福（Carrefour）今天表示，同意將中國業務80%賣給中國零售業者蘇寧易購，價格48億人民幣（台幣約216億元）。<br />\n<br />\n全球最大食品零售商之一的家樂福發表聲明指出，家樂福正在進行大型重整，中國業務估值14億歐元（台幣約495億元）。<br />\n<br />\n家樂福表示，「家樂福中國80%股權的收購價將是48億人民幣，或6.2億歐元」，這項交易預計在年底前完成。<br />\n<br />\n家樂福在1995年進軍中國，目前擁有210家大型超市和24家便利商店，去年營業額36億歐元，較2017年下滑近10%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E7%A6%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B8%E6%88%90%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A-48%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E8%B3%A3%E7%B5%A6%E8%98%87%E5%AF%A7%E6%98%93%E8%B3%BC-133502318.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25A8%2582%25E7%25A6%258F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B8%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%25AC%258A-48%25E5%2584%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E8%2598%2587%25E5%25AF%25A7%25E6%2598%2593%25E8%25B3%25BC-133502318.html&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=679b869f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E7%A6%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B8%E6%88%90%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A-48%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E8%B3%A3%E7%B5%A6%E8%98%87%E5%AF%A7%E6%98%93%E8%B3%BC-133502318.html</a>"},{"pid":"7f7c004fe10b9ae7fed780d3113a455031f4606e","tid":1254113,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:03:12.000Z","msg":"早走早著， 喺中國所有零售業 全部都遲早玩完"},{"pid":"613954af1b4dbc7e4b901c99c838e468934c2396","tid":1254113,"uid":158301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f7c004fe10b9ae7fed780d3113a455031f4606e","tid":1254113,"uid":44